name: Sakura <Flowers#2>
description:
"Every Sakura is a soul blossoming in nature"
Sakura is the beauty of the flowers, short and sweet. Symbolize beauty, renewal, optimism also joy, femininity, and even relationships. Sakura is a cheerful, optimistic, and welcoming person.

Sakura is your friend; Sakura brings optimism to your world.
Take Sakura to you and find your optimism.
